 aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">März 29, 2023</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104unu1665702620895.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/unu1665702620895.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/unu1665702620895.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"unu1665702620895\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">#startdefine\n  </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Declares the scope of precompiler constant declarations (<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">#define</span>'s)\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"unu1665702620895__topic_d93494e1_d93495e1_d93496e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"unu1665702620895__p_d93497e1_d93498e1_d93499e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">#startdefine</span>\n</p><p class=\"lines\" id=\"unu1665702620895__lines_dlx_z3d_lwb\">    <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">#define</span> <var class=\"keyword varname\">Constant</var> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>} <var class=\"keyword varname\">Expression</var></p><p class=\"lines\" id=\"unu1665702620895__lines_qjs_1jd_lwb\">   <var class=\"keyword varname\">&lt;Your code here&gt;</var></p>\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">#enddefine</span>\n<p></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"unu1665702620895__section_a4f_hjd_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d684059e88\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"unu1665702620895__p_d93503e1_d93504e1_d93505e1\">Use the\n          <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">#startdefine</span>/<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">#enddefine</span> directives to explicitly\n        define the scope of precompiler constant declarations. This is especially useful if you want\n        to define a precompiler constant that is only applicable in a specific script module, such\n        as a trigger, operation, or entity.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"unu1665702620895__p_d93506e1_d93507e1_d93508e1\">It is possible to nest\n          <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">#startdefine</span>/<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">#enddefine</span> blocks.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"unu1665702620895__section_mdz_xjd_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d684059e112\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">#startdefine</span></h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"unu1665702620895__p_d93515e1_d93516e1_d93517e1\">In the following example:</p>\n<ol class=\"ol\" id=\"unu1665702620895__ol_ijf_1kd_lwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"unu1665702620895__li_d36476e1_d36477e1_d36478e1\">An outer <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">#startdefine</span> block sets\n          the scope the <code class=\"ph codeph\">DEF1</code> declaration to two operations,\n            <code class=\"ph codeph\">myOper01</code> and <code class=\"ph codeph\">myOper02</code>. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"unu1665702620895__li_d36479e1_d36480e1_d36481e1\">An inner <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">#startdefine</span> block sets\n          the scope of the <code class=\"ph codeph\">def2</code> declaration to the <code class=\"ph codeph\">myOper02</code>\n          operation. </li>\n</ol>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104unu1665702620895_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"unu1665702620895__codeblock_xm2_dkd_lwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">;Script container\n#startdefine <sup class=\"ph sup\">1</sup>\n#define DEF1 = value1\noperation myOper01\n...\nif (something = &lt;DEF1&gt;)\n...\nendif\nend\n\n#startdefine <sup class=\"ph sup\">2</sup>\n#define DEF2 =value2\noperation myOper02\n...\nif (something = &lt;DEF2&gt;)\n...\nendif\nend\n#enddefine <sup class=\"ph sup\">2</sup>\n#enddefine <sup class=\"ph sup\">1</sup></code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616357\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616357\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "#startdefine Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 29, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 #startdefine Declares the scope of precompiler constant declarations ( #define 's) #startdefine #define Constant { = } Expression <Your code here> #enddefine Description Use the #startdefine / #enddefine directives to explicitly define the scope of precompiler constant declarations. This is especially useful if you want to define a precompiler constant that is only applicable in a specific script module, such as a trigger, operation, or entity. It is possible to nest #startdefine / #enddefine blocks. Example: Using #startdefine In the following example: An outer #startdefine block sets the scope the DEF1 declaration to two operations, myOper01 and myOper02 . An inner #startdefine block sets the scope of the def2 declaration to the myOper02 operation. Explain this code ;Script container #startdefine 1 #define DEF1 = value1 operation myOper01 ... if (something = <DEF1>) ... endif end #startdefine 2 #define DEF2 =value2 operation myOper02 ... if (something = <DEF2>) ... endif end #enddefine 2 #enddefine 1 Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}